    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Self-hosted n8n Community Edition\n\n**No Settings → Variables** on the free plan. Edit the **Config: Edit These Values** Set node (yellow fields) in each workflow instead.\n\nOptional: you can also set OS/Docker env vars on the n8n container — not required if you use the Config node.\n\n**STEP 1** Edit **Config: Edit These Values** → set `crm_outbound_webhook_secret` and `n8n_webhook_base`.\n\n**STEP 2** Activate workflow. Copy Production URL → CRM Settings → Automations → Webhook URL.\n\n**STEP 3** Import & activate sub-workflows A, B, C, Appointments (edit Config in each).",
        "height": 400,
        "width": 540,
        "color": 4
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
